    "body": "How do you calculate the \"entire balance\" ? \r\nHere's my own script to send the entire balance: \r\n```javascript\r\nfunction sendAllTx(from, to ){\r\n\tgc = new BigNumber(20e9)\r\n\tg = new BigNumber(21000)\r\n\tb = eth.getBalance(from)\r\n\tv = b.sub(gc.mul(g))\r\n\tvar tx = {from:from, to:to, gasPrice:gc, gas:g, value:v};\r\n\treturn tx;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou need to use bignumbers to get the math correct, otherwise you'll leave some dust behind, or you'll fail as above... ",
